data.title: Warner Music Entertainment
data.text:
Headed up by LA-based President, Charles Cohen, Warner Music Entertainment is a global award-winning Film, TV & content studio in the heart of WMG.

In a culture where music and visual content are intrinsically linked, our artist first, storytelling driven approach is focused on igniting audiences worldwide.

With music and entertainment at the core of every project, we develop, produce, finance and distribute content around the globe. Working with leading creative partners spanning Music, Film, TV, Live and Branded Entertainment.

We are also proud partners with award winning Producers; Imagine Entertainment, Lightbox Entertainment and SK Global Entertainment.
